{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's marvelous equipment, but it still needs to get up to speed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Demblin--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Demblin we were from 1942-- '42 to '44.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then in 1944 the Germans were realizing that the Russians are coming closer and closer, and they decided to transfer us to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I stayed pretty much hidden in the barracks most of the time because the women, the older people, went out to work so I really tried to avoid any sight.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, I mean, the Germans knew that there were children in the camp, so I just stayed in the barracks, and I played-- if there were children in my barrack, I would play with the children, sort of keep the kids in order.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I tried to avoid going out as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, come to think of it now, there was nothing to play with.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably just imaginary things that children usually make up their own imaginary things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- off-hand, I can't remember what I played with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do remember one story very vividly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My sisters brought in some potatoes, and there was a kitchen there that we could go and cook, you know, the food, if you had a potato, whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister once gave me this potato, two potatoes, to go to cook for her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all I had to do was take the potatoes, put a little bit of water in, and just boil the potatoes so they were soft.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were some women in the kitchen at that time talked me out of it, and they took away the potato.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I gave it to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said they want it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were hungry, and I gave them the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
